               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 3ra-136va)&#xD; I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 3ra-5ra)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 7ra-14va)&#xD; - On John the Evangelist as the author of
                     the book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 7ra-10rb)&#xD; -
                     Story of the family of Adam (fols. 10rb-14va)&#xD; I-3) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 42 miracles (fols. 14va-136va).</summary>
